    "description": "Every AI tool ranked. No sponsorships. No sugarcoating.\n\nChatGPT is C-tier. Famous because people are lazy, not because it’s the best. \n\nGemini? A-tier. Deep research, long context, actual intelligence. \n\nPerplexity? A-tier. Fast, sourced, no hallucination theater. \n\nCursor still leads AI coding. \n\nLovable is the non-technical founder’s cheat code. \n\nn8n feels ancient. \n\nManus got overhyped and underdelivered. \n\nAnd Seedance? S-tier. Best video generation alive right now.\n\nSave this before the tools you’re sleeping on bury you.\n#aitools #aitierlist #tierlist",
